      <title type="html">Describe a Picture - House</title>
      <link href="https://mythainote.com/describe-a-picture-house" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Describe a Picture - House" />
      <published>2019-07-01T09:01:09+00:00</published>
      <updated>2019-07-01T09:01:09+00:00</updated>
      <id>https://mythainote.com/describe-a-picture-house</id>
      <content type="html" xml:base="https://mythainote.com/describe-a-picture-house">&lt;p&gt;Welcome to that new series of stuff that I want to do to improve my Thai.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Every day I’m going to post a picture and try to describe it in Thai.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Feel free to write a comment down the page with your sentences!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;verified-sentences&quot;&gt;Verified sentences&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This sections will have the verified sentences, the one we are sure are correct in Thai, and so, I’ll add the sound to it (so we can also work on the pronunciation).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;this-is-a-house&quot;&gt;This is a house.&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;นี่คือบ้าน&lt;/span&gt; &lt;audio controls=&quot;&quot; preload=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;assets/sound/มีประตูไม้.mp3&quot;&gt;&lt;/audio&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;unverified-sentences&quot;&gt;Unverified sentences&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This sections will have all the draft sentences, I’m still not sure that everything is correct or even the sentences are just still in plain english and need to be translated.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;the-house-have-a-chimney-and-a-red-roof&quot;&gt;The house have a chimney and a red roof.&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;บ้านมีปล่องไฟและหลังคาสีแดง&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;there-is-a-wooden-door&quot;&gt;There is a wooden door.&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;มีประตูไม้&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;the-door-is-brown&quot;&gt;The door is brown.&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;ประตูเป็นสีน้ำตาล&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;there-is-a-heart-above-the-door&quot;&gt;There is a heart above the door.&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;มีใจอยู่เหนือประตู&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;there-is-a-wooden-fence-attached-to-the-house&quot;&gt;There is a wooden fence attached to the house.&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;there-are-flowers-on-the-fence&quot;&gt;There are flowers on the fence.&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;มีดอกไม้อยู่บนรั้ว&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;the-flowers-are-red-blue-and-white&quot;&gt;The flowers are red, blue and white.&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;ดอกไม้มีสีแดงสีน้ำเงินและสีขาว&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;the-grass-is-green&quot;&gt;The grass is green.&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;หญ้าเป็นสีเขียว&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;lookup-words&quot;&gt;Lookup words&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The words that I had to search from the dictionary&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;roof-หลังคา&quot;&gt;Roof: &lt;span class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;หลังคา&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;chimney-ปล่องไฟ&quot;&gt;Chimney: &lt;span class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;ปล่องไฟ&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;heart-ใจ&quot;&gt;Heart: &lt;span class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;ใจ&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;fence-รั้ว&quot;&gt;Fence: &lt;span class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;รั้ว&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;flower-ดอกไม้&quot;&gt;Flower: &lt;span class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;ดอกไม้&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;window-หน้าต่าง&quot;&gt;Window: &lt;span class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;หน้าต่าง&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;grass-หญ้า&quot;&gt;Grass: &lt;span class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;หญ้า&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;above-เหนือ---บน&quot;&gt;Above: &lt;span class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;เหนือ - บน&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;pattern-used&quot;&gt;Pattern used&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;this-is-&quot;&gt;This is …&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;นี่ คือ (Object)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

